{"tid":1149271,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔的悲歌","createTime":"2019-05-11T04:48:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T04:48:11.000Z","uid":153701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ce1155f72a3d80eca5c48ef052148dbaf2d8d4ad","tid":1149271,"uid":153701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T04:48:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔</span></span>這稱呼某程度上帶有貶義。<br />\n好多人唔會承認自己係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">連登仔</span></span>，但是會每日睇連登，每個上左熱門嘅post都睇過，但是話自己唔係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登仔</span></span>。<br />\n我有訪問過這些人，佢地話自己冇開過post，認為自己只是<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">觀眾</span></span>。<br />\n這些<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">觀眾</span></span>可能覺得自己係知識分子可以係連登明哲保身。事實上我地創作者已經用文字改變左這群<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">觀眾</span></span>的價值觀，控制他們的思考方式。<br />\n在現實生活中看看這群不承認自己是<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">連登仔</span></span>既人平日的言談，再看看手機上連登仔既留言，我才意識到我不能辨別誰是<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">連登仔</span></span></span>。"}]}